{"tid":801922,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"矮仔做gym 真係唔使咁上心","createTime":"2018-09-01T05:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T06:40:55.000Z","uid":123335,"like":42,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"74fb4aaed82fae5c56fb9a3c890cfa076e267b5e","tid":801922,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"為健康每週操1-2次，均衡飲食<br />\n係值得鼓勵既 <br />\n<br />\n但狂操爆肌，好著重線條比例<br />\n狂食supplements <br />\n真心果句<br />\n「做多左」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為... <br />\n<br />\n你始終都係矮仔<br />\n你練得越大隻，個比例越柒<br />\n<br />\n就算你練鋼條型襯返矮仔嘅比例<br />\n都係俾大隻高佬/ 鋼條型高佬 既身型屌打<br />\n<br />\n老實講<br />\n矮仔去做gym 練下肌係好事<br />\n但真係唔使太上心<br />\n<br />\n你期望越大失望越大......<br />\n付出越多, 越有入錯行嘅感覺....."},{"pid":"5d77a355bb0f93e431aff724fcdf65a6b95fbeca","tid":801922,"uid":128616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87ad4490b7cee1e02686721e1a53d7f3d3eee6f0","tid":801922,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i0.sinaimg.cn/ent/s/h/2013-05-29/U7392P28T3D3931215F326DT20130529005951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fs%2Fh%2F2013-05-29%2FU7392P28T3D3931215F326DT20130529005951.jpg&h=9d7173ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢都矮喎"},{"pid":"e300ff4440076cfb420773ae29b4b4b877e3389c","tid":801922,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d77a355bb0f93e431aff724fcdf65a6b95fbeca","tid":801922,"uid":128616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:07:34.000Z","msg":"陳奐仁肥d 反而順眼d"},{"pid":"2eb59baacc9cf8bfb6394dc79ba1469abf93ee9a","tid":801922,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"87ad4490b7cee1e02686721e1a53d7f3d3eee6f0","tid":801922,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"<i