失望越大......<br />\n付出越多, 越有入錯行嘅感覺....."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"Gym room 見到好多矮阿叔練到大大舊真係好核突"},{"pid":"e0a4512b0159c0354c2110e21c5fd1f08510411f","tid":801922,"uid":52539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"你話大隻到變型俠醫果隻都係既 冇185都CARRY唔到<br />\n<br />\n但17X矮仔有操開 正常SIZE 一定屌打 毒撚瘦仔/死肥仔<br />\n<br />\n正常睇埋佢成個人既氣場都唔同啦 有操開既份人一定唔會懶"},{"pid":"83c1cf1dca3e40eb74f0c1262d6b5a37140fe7e7","tid":801922,"uid":58316,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:15:57.000Z","msg":"矮仔做乜都柒架啦<br />\n我係女情願揀高大肚佬<br />\n都唔揀做gym矮仔<br />\n真人真事<br />\n搭地鐵有條五呎十正女<br />\n佢老公係個六呎一二肥佬<br />\n就生得個隻<br />\n個隻又毒<br />\n但正正係佢身高+肚腩+毒樣<br />\n成件事好有安全感<br />\n完全唔會覺得襯唔起條正女<br />\n反而係條正女驚佢俾人搶走<br />\n如果係條矮仔<br />\neven樣ok咩小池徹平個type<br />\n就算同條普通樣女一齊<br />\n都形住條女遲早偷食<br />\n真係爭好遠架<br />\n樣靚唔靚仔各花入各眼<br />\n今日冧你聽日就厭<br />\n但你幾高就幾高"},{"pid":"f759e2543f1c2e239493e0372d5f9e30e5f0bbcc","tid":801922,"uid":65123,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsimg.5054399.com/uploads/userup/1407/251154353292.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.5054399.com%2Fuploads%2Fuserup%2F1407%2F251154353292.jpg&h=d33801ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84597b14bcd924f2c0e93b4b7d3048e80b4c5f9b","tid":801922,"uid":35323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"kevin hart??"},{"pid":"66b19c126e6710ca805d471cde394044836dcf4f","tid":801922,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"男人矮同女人無波一樣<br />\n點練都冇用"},{"pid":"6685124553d33e7bed91c574cafa19a364544f97","tid":801922,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84597b14bcd924f2c0e93b4b7d3048e80b4c5f9b","tid":801922,"uid":35323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"kevin hart??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-0